{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "城市主題展", "storyInfo": "為了答謝解救自己的虹彩小隊，雷內爾為他們提供了住所。與此同時，住在街頭藝術社區的另一群居民正因為電視上雷內爾的大言不慚而暴跳如雷。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兄弟，仙人掌乾給我來一包，要馬可阿姨的。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬可阿姨裡面添加物不夠多，不如馬可叔叔好吃！", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少囉唆啦！總之給我來包仙人掌乾，我現在餓得要死。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你這副死人樣，一晚上沒睡吧，又在熬夜洗照片？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "靈感總是在深夜驟然降臨，我也很苦惱。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我的照片你什麼時候弄好？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……我想起來了，是你說要送人的那份？是那個玩金屬樂的女孩？", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，那女孩上個月已經把我甩了……", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惡啊，深夜裡記憶也總是會莫名消失。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*粗口*這棟樓裡那麼多攝影師，我怎麼就找上了你這個拖延症。", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喲，特克諾，回來了？那間藝術館好不好玩？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快滾蛋。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，碰壁了？你昨天晚上不是還信誓旦旦地說要去那裡塗點什麼嗎？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他那座“宮殿”裡面長什麼樣啊？我聽說裡面有不少名家真跡，早知道跟你一起去了。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別提了，我輪廓剛畫完，就有人追出來了。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#2$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖嘖。", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，這種事有一次就有無數次，總有一次他逃不掉，下次你可以帶我去。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也可以，嘿嘿。", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多夠了啊，你們兩個……老爹今天出門了嗎？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒，老爹今天心情很差，在他房間裡一天都沒出來。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜，他或許正等你的“好消息”呢。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g11_deluxeroom_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，雷內爾先生，你不認識列維。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我也得再確定一下，你也不認識我叔叔，是吧？高個子，戴眼鏡，笑得很陰森。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你再說下去，我就要懷疑你叔叔就是我們要找的人了，先生。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我想這應該只是另外一個令人不快的巧合。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_winglssice"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然誤會解釋清楚了，你們要一起來點嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想不用了，雷內爾先生，我們得走了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "IANA，你為什麼在顫抖？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們沒在做夢，沒在經歷幻覺……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要麼在時間上，要麼在空間上……被某種不可知的力量“發射”了出去，落在了這裡……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是難以想像的時間維度上的地球，也許是一顆遙遠的行星……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是很激動，ELA。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能明白你，但擺在我們面前的不僅是全然陌生的世界，還有全然陌生的問題。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以……無論你現在有多麼激動，都請冷靜下來。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……抱歉。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，朋友們，但願深夜來臨前我們能在這裡找到落腳的地方。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "氣氛倒也不必那麼惆悵吧，諸位救了我的性命，作為回報，一些幫助我還是能夠提供的。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，一個住的地方？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會吧，你們難道真的打算今晚睡在路邊的紙板上嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要下雨了。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們不會白白接受你的幫助，雷內爾先生。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這期間，我們可以負責你的安全，至少保證不會有人如今天一般，帶著武器衝進你的房間。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，或者帶著武器從天花板上掉下來——", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，米沃什，我覺得沒有問題。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）可是我們對他們的身分一無所知，雷內爾。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#10$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）那這不就是我們瞭解的機會嗎，米沃什？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）……太任性了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#10$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）你也不是第一天認識我了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你們打算拒絕的話，我建議盡快。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，女士，我沒有意見。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，趁人事部還沒下班，我們還可以去簽份正式的雇傭合約。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，迪亞茲，那個……我回來了。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，迪亞茲，我聽外面的人說你在等我。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的行動……咳咳，沒能成功，但你也可以放心，我沒受傷。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……坐下吧。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在看什麼？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喏。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾？他又在放什麼屁了？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾先生，就在您為克里斯達爾藝術館開幕式操勞的同時，一個扎根本地的社區也在籌辦一場藝術節，不知您怎麼看？", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我尊重藝術，在那裡生活的人普遍都很有想法，他們的創作也都蠻有意思的。但藝術節不是人人都能辦，他們太缺乏專業人士的參與了。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我始終認為，將雙方正在做的事情相類比是一件非常愚蠢的事情，藝術館承載的意義遠超他們的藝術節。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們將各地的藝術品匯集在多索雷斯，展現文化與藝術的多樣性，也為各方的藝術愛好者提供一個交流的平台。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於多索雷斯藝術領域的發展來說，這不是一場業餘人士的藝術節可以比擬的。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個藝術品販子竟然好意思說我們不專業？！", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#3$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他和我們不對盤又不是第一天了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#3$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他一到多索雷斯，那些見錢眼開的機構和評論家就把我們社區當成了捧他的絕佳材料。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他本人又從來不拿正眼看我們，什麼都不瞭解就敢說三道四，拿我們的創作替他自己的胡說八道當背書。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果就是我們做什麼都受阻，辦畫展，發專輯，連小型的現場演出也是。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前他不還有個所謂的社區開發計劃嗎？搞得烏煙瘴氣，最後被我們搞砸了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我們也沒給他什麼好臉色——", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，比如你，你不就跑到他藝術館外面塗鴉去了嗎？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明是他先找人在報紙上把我朋友的作品批得一文不值的……", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以他提到我們能有什麼好話？他愛說什麼就——", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到這裡，我不得不代表全多索雷斯的藝術創作者們講兩句。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼克里斯達爾藝術館能吸引這麼多目光，能取得這麼大的成就？因為我們代表了多索雷斯藝術領域真正有價值的部分。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "充分吸收多索雷斯的文化養分，表達多索雷斯這座城市真正的精神，這也是我建立克里斯達爾藝術館的最初目的……", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他要代表誰？全多索雷斯的藝術創作者？！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們幫逃離辛嘉斯王朝種植園的樂隊辦演出的時候他在幹嘛？我們翻譯新出的烏薩斯小說的時候他在幹嘛？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了坐在玻璃屋子裡談生意，他為“多索雷斯藝術領域”做過什麼？他也配代表多索雷斯？！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹，消消氣，消消氣……", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒是想消氣！知道嗎，我們的藝術節和雷內爾為那座玻璃屋子辦的開幕式撞日子了！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#4$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早上有人來告訴我這件事，我還覺得沒這麼巧，結果他剛在節目裡說了，就是同一天！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們的藝術節怎麼辦？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我懶得管他。他弄他的，我們做我們的。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們自己的進展順利，專注做自己的事情比什麼都重要。這兩天你也少去招惹他，手邊的事情要緊。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……馬特奧上尉。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回來的就只有這些人嗎？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，怎麼回事？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天……雷內爾的保鏢從天而降，阻止了我們的行動。損失了很多兄弟，我帶著剩下的人逃了出來。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們有多少人？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四個。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就四個？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四個用銃的人，訓練有素，有套很獨特的作戰方式，我們沒辦法輕易突破……", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（銃械……薩科塔嗎？之前對雷內爾的調查報告裡從未提到過啊……難道是黑鋼的人？）", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上、上尉，請您不要難為兄弟們，行動失敗的責任讓我擔就好！", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，你倒是很講義氣啊。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屬下……", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，別這麼戰戰兢兢的，講義氣又不是壞事。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出發前拿到的消息有誤，難免最後要出問題，這次行動就當是探探那傢伙的虛實了。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，那個箱子裡是錢，你拿去分給手下的人，裡面還有些賭場籌碼，好好去玩玩，贏了算你們的，輸了算我的。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上尉，您……真的？！", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "賭的時候長點心眼，那裡面人多嘴雜，你耳朵靈敏些，留意聽聽。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，聽到有價值的消息屬下一定及時彙報。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那片社區的事情……您之後打算怎麼辦？上面的人一直在催，我們的娛樂城開發計劃就差這一片了。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也只能另想辦法了，既然雷內爾是鐵板一塊，不如直接從社區入手。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題，我會格外為您留意那裡的消息。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好幹，等到娛樂城在那裡建起來了，我可是屬意你去做管理人的，別讓我覺得自己看走了眼。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您的栽培！", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g5_galleries", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這幾天來得都比我想像中要早些，ELA小姐。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我喜歡早一點到，因為我不喜歡讓別人等太久。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很抱歉，我來晚了，路上稍微有些塞。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九點整，還可以，不算太晚。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前我也算是個守時的人，但來到這裡後，發現大家都喜歡比約定的時間來得稍微晚一些。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，等待的時間裡正好看看這裡的展品。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座藝術館……至少在光源的設計上很獨特。白天用自然光源，到了晚上仍然亮得像白晝一樣。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你喜歡藝術？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，只是有興趣。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工作之餘，你可以多來看看，等到克里斯達爾藝術館正式對外開放後，恐怕就沒有這樣好的機會了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，在這裡工作沒有免費的票可以拿嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然有，員工福利的一部分。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的意思其實是，現在還沒有擁擠的客流，你可以一直駐足在喜歡的作品前而不被任何人打擾，很難得。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可有時影響參觀者心情的未必是吵鬧的遊客，一幅令人心裡發毛的畫作也可以。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你是說盡頭處的那幅嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那其實不是名家作品，是雷內爾父親的畫像。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#9$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了他留下來的東西，我們才能來到異國他鄉修建起這座展館，並將整個泰拉的藝術佳作都匯集在其中。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，雷內爾一直覺得很有必要做點什麼來紀念他的父親。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如在這裡掛一幅巨大的畫像？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾只是想確保所有人都能第一眼看見老先生的模樣。況且，只是一幅畫像而已，我和雷內爾都覺得，老先生值得更多。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#9$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔……他還真是孝順的好孩子。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，ELA小姐，時間差不多了，我也該帶你去找他了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g7_galleriesstaircase", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直想問，為什麼每次到他頂樓的辦公室都要爬樓梯？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不喜歡別人來找他的時候一點體力都不費，最起碼得走一層樓梯，所有人都一樣。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我可沒看過他自己爬樓梯。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有自己的專用電梯。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里斯達爾藝術館的高層辦公區就只有這麼一部電梯，樓梯也只有我們現在正在走的這一部。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呵，真是天才般的想法。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯一的好處是，我們需要布置守衛的範圍縮小了不少。其他詳細事項呢？你還有要交代的嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒，需要交代你做的事情只有一件，別讓他死掉就好。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚上呢？需要小隊成員輪換嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不需要，因為晚上有我在。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}